{"tid":617070,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有個細路話自己“好開心”嗰條片","createTime":"2018-04-04T16:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T07:06:24.000Z","uid":19592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8f5eb2733922217952f7b1d9c18ab6daaae65e","tid":617070,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"有條片係訪問啲怪獸家長，<br />\n之後個家長話幫小朋友報咗好多補習班，<br />\n基本上冇得休息。<br />\n然後記者問小朋友開唔開心，<br />\n之後個媽媽就煩似話&ldquo;佢好開心㗎佢好開心㗎講畀姐姐聽。&ldquo;<br />\n然後個朋友就講咗句&ldquo;好開心&rdquo;， 但完全冇靈魂。<br />\n<br />\n好想搵返條片，有冇人有。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665ccf3320a75fa03a15966bf8d96a8baf390e04","tid":617070,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:03:52.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"b97fc88d75b801c5ba2f33a482b24fddeba98e24","tid":617070,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929f68e4dc7265029849b4f9f781c47d2fd44c59","tid":617070,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:10:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4e9bbb40352d5bb171282ae56d29c7725dfb774","tid":617070,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"推"}]}